<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/15851>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Tokay gecko (Gekko gecko). Adult male from Same, Manufahi District (USNM 573671, SVL 142 mm, TL 236 mm; top) and juvenile Gekko gecko from Wailakurini, Viqueque District (USNM 573673, SVL 88 mm, TL 168 mm; bottom). Note the brownish, regenerated tail on the adult (top). Photos by Mark O'Shea (top) and Hinrich Kaiser (bottom)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/15851" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

